<section style="padding-left: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">
<h2>Empowering parents</h2>
<p>GreatSchools is the leading national nonprofit empowering parents to unlock educational opportunities for their child.</p>
<p>GreatSchools’ trusted ratings and school information help parents find the right school for their family and improve schools in their communities. The thousands of articles, tips and interactive tools help parents support their child’s learning and wellbeing every day.</p>
<p>Families, community leaders and policy-makers turn to GreatSchools for the school information they need to guide children to great futures.<br>
</p>

<section style="padding-left: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">
<div class="row" style="padding-left: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">
