<h4 style="margin-bottom: 3px; margin-top: 10px;">Community action</h4>
<p>When it comes to community action, we offer on-the-ground organizers and advocacy groups, tools, and information to push for better schools for all kids.</p>
</div>

<div class="col-sm-4" style="padding-left: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">
